    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['30/IMG_1500'], right: ['30/IMG_1501'] })
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: 'Looks the same mid afternoon, as it does at 1am in the morning.', photo: '30/IMG_1515'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['30/IMG_1526'], right: ['30/IMG_1535','30/IMG_1546'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Eventually, we left Paris Las Vegas, and continued our way back to the Monte Carlo.

  = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '30/IMG_1556'})

  .Content
    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Later that evening, we headed out to the Rainforest cafÃ© for dinner.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/place_restaurant", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '29/DSC02410', title: 'Rainforest cafÃ©', address: '3717 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas', price: '$$', menu: 'American', rating: 2, link: '' })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Itâ€™s certainly the sort of place that trades more on the experience than the cuisine, but it was a very pleasant meal.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['30/IMG_1626'], right: ['30/IMG_1632', '30/IMG_1628'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We were all a little exhausted from a long day.

          Richard stayed out to get some photos of Vegas at night. Many of the rest of us retired to bed early to catch up on some sleep.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: 'Good night, vegas.', photo: 'banner'})

    .Row#july-31
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          ---

          I awoke early the next day. Everyone else was still asleep. I decided that I might set off on my own and try to do some souvenir shopping today.

          I headed down to the starbucks and grabbed their porridge for breakfast.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_grid", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, rows: [ { count: 2, caption: 'It was actually pretty good.', photos: ['31/IMG_2975','31/IMG_2976'] } ] } )

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          After a quick breakfast, I found a souvenir gift shop that sounded suitable for gifts for my family, and so I headed off.

          I headed for the Aria Express station on the upper floors of the Monte Carlo.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '31/IMG_2977'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          I alighted at the Belagio.

          The Belagio has a very luxurious interior. I walked past a dessert place with presumably realy chocolate foundout prominently displayed pouring down glass leaves.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, right: ['31/IMG_2993'], left: ['31/IMG_2982','31/IMG_2987'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          I headed out of the Belagio and made my way to a bus stop, where I boarded a double decker bus.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '31/IMG_2995'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          I consulted my destination on Google maps as the bus pulled away.

          The bus continued down the strip of Vegas that Richard, Butcher and I had trekked yesterday. The scale seemed a little smaller from the vantage point of the bus, as we were whisked away from the main strip.

          The bus headed west. I alighted at a nearby stop, on to a street with a very different vibe from the Vegas strip that we had just come from.

