      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Unfortunately, the shop I appeared to be looking for was not at the address I arrived at.

          I continued to walk, and luckily came across another novelty gift shop.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['31/IMG_3021'], right: ['31/IMG_3023'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Gifts in tow, I head back towards the main strip.

          Now early afternoon, I grab a burrito for lunch, and try an all-American Choco Taco for dessert.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['31/IMG_3028','31/IMG_3032'], right: ['31/IMG_3033'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          After lunch, I met up with the others as the hotel.

          Andrew, Irwin, Jared, Butcher and I head to the pool. Richard goes to try his hand at poker (and wins $200).

          ---

          That evening, we set off to see Penn & Teller at the Rio casino.

          We opted to walk there, so we head off early evening, planning to get dinner nearby.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['31/DSC02590','31/IMG_3041'], right: ['31/DSC02588','31/DSC02592'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Once we arrived, we grabbed a quick dinner at the Rio food court.

          Soon enough, it was time for the show.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '31/IMG_3059'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          After the show, we managed to get photos with Penn Jillette.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['31/DSC02613'], right: ['31/DSC02614'] })  

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We made our way back towards the main Vegas strip.

          I suggested we take a detour through Bellagio, having been quite impressed by its architecture that morning.
      
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['31/DSC02631'], right: ['31/DSC02618','31/DSC02629'] })  

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We retired to our apartment, and got some shut eye, ahead of our departure to Colorado the following day.
          
    .Row#august-01
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          ---

          The next morning, we awoke, and finished our last minute packing.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, right: ['01/IMG_3094'], left: ['01/IMG_3096','01/IMG_3097'] })  

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We then checked out, and boarded a bus for the airport.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '>that feel when leaving Vegas', photo: '01/IMG_3100'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Soon enough, we arrived at the Las Vegas aiport.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: 'There were even slot machines here, in case you needed your fix.', photo: '01/IMG_3118'})

    .Row
